#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int c;
    long long int x,y,t,a,b;
    while(1)
    {
    a=1;
    b=2;
    c=0;
    scanf("%lld%lld",&x,&y);
    if((x==0)&&(y==0))
        break;
    while(1)
    {
            t=a+b;
            a=b;
            b=t;
            if((t>=x)&&(t<=y))
                c++;
            if(t>=y)
                break;
    }
    printf("%d\n",c);
    }
    return 0;
}
